{
  "texts": [
    "Prior to collecting stroke data, we asked participants to hit a shuttlecock toward the center of the court.",
    "By analyzing the landing position of the shuttlecock, we gathered information on the accuracy of the player's stroke.",
    "As mentioned in the Dataset Design section, coaches often use the trajectory of the shuttlecock to evaluate a player's training process and provide feedback.",
    "To capture the shuttlecock's trajectory, we installed a camera to record the launch position, the participant, and the trajectory of the shuttlecock.",
    "Further, videos were recorded using Pupil Invisible glasses to determine the precise location of the shuttlecock landing."
  ]
}